data.description: This spectacular country home with 3000 sq ft of living area was recently renovated in 2021 and is ready to move into. A beautiful and serene setting awaits overlooking a large pond. The house has an open layout with a very large living room and kitchen and everyone will enjoy the family room/game room.  Plenty of space is available in the huge 1700 Sq Foot garage/workshop, with 4 oversized garage doors. An additional  900 Sq ft work shed is next to the house.  Get ready to barbecue on the 1500 square foot back patio. Don't wait, come see this beautiful home before it is gone!
